title: Cafe at ARTpool Gallery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A relaxed and fun cafe which is a part of a larger business which includes local art, vintage clothing, antiques, vinyl records, monthly events, and much more. Dishes are made-in-house. Primary focus is lunch and offers vegan and gluten free choices. As of Sept 2013, does not offer any vegan or gluten free desserts. Menu items include salads, soups, sandwiches, wraps and more. Free Wi-Fi. Small-pet friendly.
